         <div type="translation" resp="part:vito">
             <p>Success! In the 6th year of King <persName type="human" subtype="coronation">Vāsiṭṭhīputta Siri-Sātakaṇṇi</persName>, on the 4th fortnight of the hot season, on the 5th day. A straight slab and four uprights are a pious gift <supplied reason="subaudible">made</supplied> by  the caravan leader <persName type="human"><roleName type="merchant" subtype="donor">Samaṇa</roleName></persName> (Skt. <foreign xml:lang="san-Latn">Śramaṇa</foreign>?), in honour of all buddhas, in honour of his father and mother, and for the well-being and happiness of the whole world.</p>
             <!--translation encoded as per EGD §9.2 -->
